00:19:15,200 --> 00:19:19,670
Xiao Chun Hua, rest assured! Older Brother will secretly protect you.

247
00:19:21,030 --> 00:19:22,910
Then I'll return now.

248
00:19:22,910 --> 00:19:27,170
Gu Xingzhu, escort Chun Hua back to Fengming Mountain Manor.

249
00:19:27,170 --> 00:19:28,740
Yes.

250
00:19:32,580 --> 00:19:35,600
Put me down! I want to get down.

251
00:19:35,600 --> 00:19:37,400
Let go!

252
00:19:40,800 --> 00:19:45,700
Gu Xingzhu, can we choose a more civilized mode of transportation?

253
00:19:45,700 --> 00:19:49,980
You carry me like a sack. It's not comfortable at all.

254
00:19:49,980 --> 00:19:54,230
Miss Chun Hua, you probably forgot your own identity.

255
00:19:55,260 --> 00:19:57,360
What identity?

256
00:19:57,360 --> 00:20:01,350
I'm your Cave Master Shangguan's little sister!

257
00:20:03,280 --> 00:20:06,730
I am just following the rules.

258
00:20:08,940 --> 00:20:10,840
Then let me ask you.

259
00:20:10,840 --> 00:20:13,210
Did Cave Master Shangguan and I

260
00:20:13,210 --> 00:20:16,300
- really have the same mother and father? 
 - It's getting late.

261
00:20:19,670 --> 00:20:22,010
Find a horse carriage for my little sister.

262
00:20:22,010 --> 00:20:23,950
Yes, Cave Master.

263
00:20:28,830 --> 00:20:30,900
Am I really your biological sister?

264
00:20:30,900 --> 00:20:34,590
My request isn't too much to ask. Is it that hard to fulfill?

265
00:20:35,570 --> 00:20:37,760
Indeed, you are not.

266
00:20:38,680 --> 00:20:41,150
It's possible that Mom and Dad misremembered.

267
00:20:41,150 --> 00:20:44,780
Chun Hua could be Qiu Yue's older sister.

268
00:20:48,930 --> 00:20:52,370
I, Shangguan Chun Hua,

269
00:20:52,370 --> 00:20:55,470
am Shangguan Qiu Yue's older sister!

270
00:21:04,970 --> 00:21:06,860
What are you doing?

271
00:21:06,860 --> 00:21:09,270
Aren't you suspicious?

272
00:21:09,270 --> 00:21:13,290
Then, how about I'll take off my clothes

273
00:21:13,290 --> 00:21:16,070
and show you my birthmark?

274
00:21:17,110 --> 00:21:19,280
I wasn't serious!

275
00:21:22,900 --> 00:21:25,790
I am your older brother.  What are you afraid of?

276
00:21:30,160 --> 00:21:31,860
Xiao Bai!

277
00:21:37,010 --> 00:21:39,650
I didn't think even Older Brother would fall for it.

278
00:21:46,700 --> 00:21:50,480
Older Brother, do you resemble Father or Mother?

279
00:21:50,480 --> 00:21:53,070
- Why? 
 - Although we are siblings,

280
00:21:53,070 --> 00:21:56,570
I can't find any similarities between us.

281
00:21:56,570 --> 00:21:59,840
Did you inherit all of Father and Mother's good traits?

282
00:21:59,840 --> 00:22:02,070
How does Older Brother compare with Xiao Bai?

283
00:22:02,070 --> 00:22:06,860
Compare Brother and Husband? Of course, they're different.

284
00:22:09,800 --> 00:22:13,100
To me, you two are different.

285
00:22:14,740 --> 00:22:16,670
How are we different?

286
00:22:18,290 --> 00:22:20,810
Older Brother Qiu Yue is a close relative.

287
00:22:20,810 --> 00:22:23,440
If I had merely half of Older Brother's good looks,

288
00:22:23,440 --> 00:22:26,610
the Xin Fa would come easily to me.

289
00:22:26,610 --> 00:22:31,240
If you say it like that, Xiao Chun Hua wants to use the beauty trap.

290
00:22:31,240 --> 00:22:33,120
He is a gentleman.

291
00:22:33,120 --> 00:22:36,490
I don't know if the beauty trap will work.

292
00:22:39,840 --> 00:22:43,500
It's entirely Older Brother Qiu Yue's fault for stealing all the good looks.

293
00:22:43,500 --> 00:22:48,020
If not, the beauty trap would work, wouldn't it?

294
00:22:48,970 --> 00:22:53,710
Xiao Chun Hua is right so we have to find another way.

295
00:22:54,370 --> 00:22:55,990
Also,

296
00:22:57,070 --> 00:22:59,220
you aren't allowed to use the beauty trap.

297
00:22:59,220 --> 00:23:01,590
You'll make a spectacle of yourself.

298
00:23:01,590 --> 00:23:04,170
I don't need Older Brother's reminder.

299
00:23:16,610 --> 00:23:18,300
[Thousand Moon Cave]

300
00:23:19,170 --> 00:23:22,690
Master, I wonder if Miss Chun Hua is Hua Xiaolei.

301
00:23:22,690 --> 00:23:26,710
Whether she is Hua Xiaolei or not, why are you so nervous?

302
00:23:26,710 --> 00:23:29,810
I have absolutely no intention of prying. It just that...

303
00:23:30,640 --> 00:23:35,590
I'm guessing, letting Miss Chun Hua go and steal the Xin Fa.

304
00:23:35,590 --> 00:23:40,740
But it's related to the matter of Xiao Bai not mastering the Fengming Saber.

305
00:23:41,940 --> 00:23:44,000
You're quick to listen and observe.

306
00:23:44,000 --> 00:23:47,620
- For the sake of Cave Master's safety. 
 - Is it for my safety?

307
00:23:51,330 --> 00:23:55,460
People without eyes and ears are the safest.

308
00:23:55,460 --> 00:23:58,500
I am wrong!  Please have mercy, Cave Master!

309
00:23:59,350 --> 00:24:01,890
I told Gu Xingzhu.

310
00:24:01,890 --> 00:24:05,560
Other than him, no one else knows.

311
00:24:07,170 --> 00:24:09,710
I'm willing to guarantee with my life.

312
00:24:12,560 --> 00:24:15,370
- There's one more thing. 
 - Say it!

313
00:24:16,180 --> 00:24:19,630
Qin Liufeng is heading toward Fengming Mountain Village.

314
00:24:21,240 --> 00:24:25,100
However, he has not met Hua Xiaolei.

315
00:24:25,570 --> 00:24:28,270
Go! Watch closely.

316
00:24:28,270 --> 00:24:29,880
Yes.

317
00:25:10,220 --> 00:25:12,080
Miss, what's wrong?

318
00:25:13,730 --> 00:25:18,250
If you encounter someone from the Demon Sect, what will you do?

319
00:25:18,250 --> 00:25:20,190
What do you do?

320
00:25:20,190 --> 00:25:21,840
Good and evil are irreconcilable!

321
00:25:21,840 --> 00:25:25,500
Getting rid of the evil is my family's duty.  Why bother asking?

322
00:25:25,500 --> 00:25:28,780
What if this person is your friend?

323
00:25:28,780 --> 00:25:31,000
Friend?  Who?

324
00:25:31,000 --> 00:25:33,260
Then what if... I'm just saying what if...

325
00:25:33,260 --> 00:25:37,410
Don't speak nonsense! I do not conspire with those who are of different beliefs.

326
00:25:37,410 --> 00:25:39,590
I will not have such a friend.

327
00:25:39,590 --> 00:25:43,080
One side is my moody older brother.

328
00:25:43,080 --> 00:25:46,250
The other side is the persistent Xiao Bai.

329
00:25:46,250 --> 00:25:48,580
What should I do?

330
00:25:48,580 --> 00:25:51,880
Forget it, forget it! Stop thinking about it.

331
00:25:51,880 --> 00:25:53,400
What's wrong?

332
00:26:02,520 --> 00:26:05,950
The sunset today is quite beautiful.

333
00:26:08,280 --> 00:26:10,140
It is indeed very beautiful.

334
00:26:10,140 --> 00:26:12,240
I never noticed it before.

335
00:26:12,240 --> 00:26:14,510
Have you never noticed?

336
00:26:15,060 --> 00:26:19,030
All four seasons, rain or shine,

337
00:26:19,030 --> 00:26:22,030
Father always tells me to practice swordsmanship.

338
00:26:23,470 --> 00:26:27,630
Xiao Bai, your life is too boring.

339
00:26:28,110 --> 00:26:31,890
Actually, what I mean is...

340
00:26:31,890 --> 00:26:35,380
do you want to put down the sword in your hand

341
00:26:35,380 --> 00:26:38,640
and watch the sunset glow with me?

342
00:26:38,640 --> 00:26:42,330
If you are bored, then go back now.

343
00:26:46,840 --> 00:26:51,730
Xiao Bai, you are really an unromantic block of wood!

344
00:27:05,280 --> 00:27:07,210
How did that happen?

345
00:27:08,120 --> 00:27:11,840
I changed to a new move. I feel it's not bad.

346
00:27:14,310 --> 00:27:15,840
Why didn't you do it according to the requirements?

347
00:27:15,840 --> 00:27:18,650
If you cut them like this, how can they become firewood?

348
00:27:18,650 --> 00:27:20,300
Firewood?

349
00:27:24,120 --> 00:27:27,180
Anyway, you've done blade work before.

350
00:27:27,180 --> 00:27:29,170
Not burning it, will be a waste, won't it?

351
00:27:29,170 --> 00:27:32,190
Are you asking me to use the Fengming Saber to gather firewood?

352
00:27:32,190 --> 00:27:35,960
I'm not! Isn't this a chance to practice your swordsmanship?

353
00:27:35,960 --> 00:27:38,020
Once you're done practicing,

354
00:27:38,020 --> 00:27:41,270
you can bring the wood to the kitchen to burn.

355
00:27:41,270 --> 00:27:43,970
The Xiao clan's Fengming Saber punishes evil and rewards good.

356
00:27:43,970 --> 00:27:47,620
It has a good reputation everywhere but is tarnished by you.

357
00:27:49,430 --> 00:27:52,820
How can you refer to it like that?

358
00:27:52,820 --> 00:27:55,940
If you don't gather firewood, you must gather bamboo. Isn't that the same?

359
00:27:55,940 --> 00:27:58,100
How is it the same?

360
00:28:01,150 --> 00:28:04,300
Are you scared that the Fengming Saber will become blunt?

361
00:28:04,300 --> 00:28:08,250
- Then I'll just find you a normal blade some other day. 
 - You...

362
00:28:08,250 --> 00:28:11,060
Also, why are you learning martial arts?

363
00:28:11,060 --> 00:28:14,500
- Shouldn't it be practical? 
 - Martial arts isn't used for gathering firewood.

364
00:28:14,500 --> 00:28:16,390
I know!

365
00:28:16,390 --> 00:28:19,750
But... really, don't you think that

366
00:28:19,750 --> 00:28:21,510
using martial arts to cut firewood

367
00:28:21,510 --> 00:28:24,930
can save time while practicing swordsmanship?

368
00:28:30,610 --> 00:28:34,040
Xiao Bai! Xiao Bai!

369
00:28:34,040 --> 00:28:36,160
Your swordsmanship is so good.

370
00:28:36,160 --> 00:28:38,620
Can you teach me a few tricks?

371
00:28:39,210 --> 00:28:41,830
Swordsmanship is a steady skill, and requires strength.

372
00:28:41,830 --> 00:28:45,480
Women are naturally weaker. Using a saber proves to be difficult.

373
00:28:45,480 --> 00:28:48,400
If Miss really wants to learn, I'll teach you the sword.

374
00:28:48,400 --> 00:28:50,870
No need, no need! I don't need to learn much.

375
00:28:50,870 --> 00:28:54,410
- I just want to learn a few tricks. 
 - A few tricks?

376
00:28:54,410 --> 00:28:56,810
Yes, it's just for gathering firewood.

377
00:29:10,240 --> 00:29:12,250
Don't understanding human natures,

378
00:29:12,250 --> 00:29:14,720
