379
00:29:14,720 --> 00:29:18,220
Why is my male lead like this?

380
00:29:28,500 --> 00:29:30,500
Miss Chun Hua.

381
00:29:32,520 --> 00:29:34,240
The kitchen doesn't need any more firewood.

382
00:29:34,240 --> 00:29:36,490
Master Xiao also doesn't need anyone.

383
00:29:36,490 --> 00:29:38,400
You don't have to make the effort next time.

384
00:29:38,400 --> 00:29:41,030
Did Xiao Bai make you say that?

385
00:29:43,880 --> 00:29:46,540
This brainless, wooden man.

386
00:29:50,900 --> 00:29:53,150
Are you also mocking me?

387
00:29:54,920 --> 00:29:56,650
Bow down!

388
00:29:57,230 --> 00:30:01,400
- Bow down. 
 - Is Miss training the flowers?

389
00:30:07,660 --> 00:30:10,400
This way of practicing martial arts is interesting.

390
00:30:10,400 --> 00:30:13,150
May I ask whom Miss learns from?

391
00:30:13,150 --> 00:30:14,970
I...

392
00:30:16,560 --> 00:30:18,440
Why do you care?

393
00:30:18,440 --> 00:30:21,370
If I didn't guess wrong, Miss would be

394
