396
00:30:31,030 --> 00:30:33,770
Do you know Xiao Bai?

397
00:30:33,770 --> 00:30:35,810
Xiao Bai?

398
00:30:35,810 --> 00:30:37,570
You two are so close.

399
00:30:37,570 --> 00:30:40,880
It seems that your relationship with Young Master is not ordinary.

400
00:30:41,800 --> 00:30:44,830
I was disrespectful. Sorry!

401
00:30:45,640 --> 00:30:47,490
My surname is Qin, called Liufeng.

402
00:30:47,490 --> 00:30:49,680
My father is the Dongshan Sect leader, Qin Daoxian.

403
00:30:49,680 --> 00:30:54,010
- May I ask for your beautiful name? 
 - Chun Hua.

404
00:30:54,010 --> 00:30:56,000
Chun Hua.

405
00:30:56,000 --> 00:30:57,860
The romantic flowers in spring.

406
00:30:57,860 --> 00:31:01,730
It seems that Miss lives up to this name.

407
00:31:10,720 --> 00:31:13,010
You, too.

