00:31:19,430 --> 00:31:21,190
Junior Brother Qin.

411
00:31:21,940 --> 00:31:23,850
Young Master.

412
00:31:25,040 --> 00:31:27,240
Xiao Bai, you're here!

413
00:31:30,950 --> 00:31:32,780
Young Master.

414
00:31:46,090 --> 00:31:49,870
It's been a while, yet Senior Brother Xiao still looks so grand.

